{"tid":600963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"交通警被貨車撞倒 送院不治","createTime":"2018-03-21T22:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T02:13:05.000Z","uid":90978,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"60aeee0d20356840cc4db40c832d13f890ff711e","tid":600963,"uid":90978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T22:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180322&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57978868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180322%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57978868&d=ScNoREVfi3KSywTWTNd69xOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=0fcc117a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180322%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57978868&h=52a81c93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180322&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57978868</a><br />\n<br />\n東九龍走廊發生嚴重車禍，凌晨約4時45分，一輛平治沿東九龍走廊往尖沙嘴行駛，至漆咸道北分界，撞向路中分隔路牌，意外中無人受傷。警方西九龍交通部一輛警車到場處理。<br />\n<br />\n至清晨5時24分，一輛輕型密斗貨車沿東九龍走廊駛至，猛撞向警車及旁邊的交通警，交通警頭部重創昏迷，現場遺下一條向血路。救護員到場將交通警送院搶救，惜終於不治。警方封鎖現場調查。受車禍影響，東九龍走廊天橋西行線往紅磡方向暫時全線封閉。"},{"pid":"ec2d29654335a11d20772fc6325266890f403aab","tid":600963,"uid":1134,"like":7,"dislike":35,"score":-28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T22:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/063740_10e2347acf9ea80f111ba05d4a23321f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F063740_10e2347acf9ea80f111ba05d4a23321f.png&h=8de1f6c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警察叔叔好眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45050e3d3f8d93020b08de9d8abbf7eb8d1e330e","tid":600963,"uid":48112,"like":13,"dislike":12,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"reply